name: Invesco FTSE RAFI U.S. Index ETF II
longDescription: PXS seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI US 1000 Index, or any successor thereto, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units. Invesco FTSE RAFI U.S. Index ETF II (the ETF) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI US 1000 Index or any successor thereto.
fulldescription: PXS seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI US 1000 Index, or any successor thereto, on an unhedged basis, in the case of any unhedged units, or on a hedged basis, in the case of any hedged units. Invesco FTSE RAFI U.S. Index ETF II (the ETF) seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI US 1000 Index or any successor thereto. This Invesco ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in U.S. equity securities with the highest fundamental weightings using the Fundamental Index methodology developed by Research Affiliates, LLC.
